  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the broccoli florets and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the chickpeas, tomato puree, garam masala, smoked paprika, and salt to the pan and stir well.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bamboo steamer and steam for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the smoky Indian broccoli chana masala hot, garnished with chopped cilantro."
